title: Top Floor 1 Bedroom 1 Bath With Large Balcony
posting_body: ['Live on the Park.', ' Urban comforts, outdoor living right.', 'Wander trails along the waterfront.', 'Wrap yourself in luxury.', 'Wake up every day to the wild-hearted beauty of the Pacific Northwest – it’s right outside your window at Bell Marymoor Park.', 'From our free-spirited rooftop deck to the light-filled arboretum, every element is designed to enhance your indoor/outdoor lifestyle.', 'Roam far in your own backyard when you live next door to Marymoor Park, an immense green playground for recreation and relaxation.', 'We’re directly on the bike trail and just a few minutes away from Downtown Redmond and East Lake Sammamish.', '-Quartz Countertops', '-Fully equipped collaboration room', '-Keyless', 'Entry', '-Brevvie - briefly rent everything system', '-High Ceilings in all First Floor Homes', '-Bocce ball, shuffle board, life-sized scrabble and mega jenga', '-640 acres of outdoor recreation possibilities at your doorstep', '-24-hour package lockers', '-Energy-Star Stainless Appliance Package', '-LED Lighting Package', '-Generous Closet Space', '-Complimentary starbucks coffee machine', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and Specials subject to change daily and restrictions may apply.', 'Please contact leasing agent for details.']
